snippet.title: How To Make Jurassic Park Amber (DIY)
snippet.description:
New uploads every Tuesday or so. You can help me make these videos by following these links: 
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/user?u=42084
My Etsy Store: https://www.etsy.com/shop/WilliamJakespeare?ref=shop_sugg
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/william_jakespeare_props/

William Jakespeare Builds: 
Kryptonite: https://youtu.be/2xS2UAUvolc
Knights of Ren Helmet: https://youtu.be/j25Ze_5clWA
Lightsaber: https://youtu.be/sBN-mjwkZJQ
5th Element ZF1: https://youtu.be/W-vgHjITfjs
Battle Droid: https://youtu.be/Q-foCzYK4gE
Rogue One Helmet: https://youtu.be/p-7gDYJnpa0
Kylo Ren Helmet: https://youtu.be/p17pyI9PIQQ
Fallout Pip Boy: https://youtu.be/2aPiKKuZ2xQ
Wooden Bender: https://youtu.be/W4dvaLbS7Po

Tools/Materials List: 
• Universal Mold Release 
• Silicone  
• Dixie Cups 
• Sand paper
• Rotary tool 
• Fishing Lure 
• Resin
• Resin Dye
• Scissors
• Razor pens
• Box Cutter
• Sharpening Stone 
• Belt Sander
• Gloss Enamel 

Additional music by Kevin MacLeod available at:
http://www.incompetech.com/music/royalty-free/
